videos.description: Alertique Gilbert drives the lane and dishes a pass at the last second to Isaiah Whaley who jams it down on the baseline.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Gilbert's silky smooth pass leads to Whaley's baseline slam for UConn) 2020/01/23 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Gilbert's silky smooth pass leads to Whaley's baseline slam for UConn

videos.description: UConn freshman James Bouknight comes down with the rebound and takes it the rest of the way himself, through four Houston defenders for the layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Bouknight grabs the rebound and goes end-to-end for the lay-in) 2020/01/23 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Bouknight grabs the rebound and goes end-to-end for the lay-in

videos.description: DeJon Jarreau comes up with the steal for Houston and pushes the ball forward to Cedrick Alley Jr. who slams it home.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Alley slams one down off the break) 2020/01/23 ESHEETS

videos.headline: Alley slams one down off the break

videos.description: Dan Hurley wants a technical foul called on Houston for taunting, but in turn the referees call one on the UConn bench instead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (UConn wanted taunting on Houston but gets one themselves) 2020/01/23 ESHEETS

videos.headline: UConn wanted taunting on Houston but gets one themselves

videos.description: Alterique Gilbert hits a big 3-pointer from the top of the key and puts finger to mouth to shush the Houston crowd.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Gilbert hits the 3-ball and shushes the Houston crowd) 2020/01/23 ESHEETS
